{"id":"fellowship","term":"Fellowship","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>(1.) With God, consisting in the knowledge of his will (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Job 22:21\">Job 22:21</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"John 17:3\">John 17:3</a>); agreement with his designs (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Amos 3:2\">Amos 3:2</a>); mutual affection (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Romans 8\">Rom. 8</a>: 38, 39); enjoyment of his presence (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Psalms 4:6\">Ps. 4:6</a>); conformity to his image (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 John 2:6\">1 John 2:6</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 John 1:6\">1:6</a>); and participation of his felicity (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 John 1:3\">1 John 1:3</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 John 1:4\">4</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Ephesians 3:14\">Eph. 3:14-21</a>).</p>\n<p>(2.) Of saints with one another, in duties (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Romans 12:5\">Rom. 12:5</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Corinthians 12:1\">1 Cor. 12:1</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Thessalonians 5:17\">1 Thess. 5:17</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Thessalonians 5:18\">18</a>); in ordinances (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Hebrews 10:25\">Heb. 10:25</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Acts 2:46\">Acts 2:46</a>); in grace, love, joy, etc. (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Malachi 3:16\">Mal. 3:16</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Corinthians 8:4\">2 Cor. 8:4</a>); mutual interest, spiritual and temporal (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Romans 12:4\">Rom. 12:4</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Romans 12:13\">13</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Hebrews 13:16\">Heb. 13:16</a>); in sufferings (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Romans 15:1\">Rom. 15:1</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Romans 15:2\">2</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Galatians 6:1\">Gal. 6:1</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Galatians 6:2\">2</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Romans 12:15\">Rom. 12:15</a>; and in glory (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Revelation 7:9\">Rev. 7:9</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Job 22:21","John 17:3","Amos 3:2","Romans 8","Psalms 4:6","1 John 2:6","1 John 1:6","1 John 1:3","1 John 1:4","Ephesians 3:14","Romans 12:5","1 Corinthians 12:1","1 Thessalonians 5:17","1 Thessalonians 5:18","Hebrews 10:25","Acts 2:46","Malachi 3:16","2 Corinthians 8:4","Romans 12:4","Romans 12:13","Hebrews 13:16","Romans 15:1","Romans 15:2","Galatians 6:1","Galatians 6:2","Romans 12:15","Revelation 7:9"]}